==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-əʊnəʊ|-əʊnəʊ]]

===Noun phrase===
'''no-no'''
#(''informal'') Something that is [[forbidden]], [[prohibited]], [[discouraged]].
#:''Smoking indoors is becoming a real '''no-no''' these days, in many places.''
#{{baseball}} A no-hitter, a game in which no batter on one of the teams got a [[hit]]
#: ''He threw two '''no-nos''' in his career.''
#{{baseball}} A no hitter, a game in which no batter on one of the teams has gotten a hit yet
#: ''He's throwing a '''no-no'''.''